lead_paragraph: Jonathan Lucroy drove in three runs and the Milwaukee Brewers earned a 5-4 victory over the reeling Cincinnati Reds on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Villar, Lucroy Spark Brewers in 5-4 Win Over Reeling Reds
